# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok tony raines will drive in his first nascar sprint cup race of the season sunday , ### miles around the grinding , high-banked concrete track in dover , del. .
# ::alignments
(d / drive-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Raines")
            :mod (t / ton))
      :subevent-of (r / race-02
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG3 (c / cup
                  :ARG1-of (s / sprint-02)
                  :mod (c2 / company
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Nascar"))
                  :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                        :value 1))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / sunday))
            :location (a / around
                  :op1 (t2 / track
                        :ARG1-of (g / grind-01)
                        :ARG1-of (b / bank-01
                              :ARG1-of (h / high-02))
                        :mod (c3 / concrete)
                        :location (c4 / city
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Dover"))))
            :duration (d3 / distance-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (m / mile))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok last time the los angeles lakers entered hostile territory with a series tied , the location was the alamodome , the round was the western conference finals and the tie was #-# .
# ::alignments
(m / multi-sentence
      :snt1 (e / enter-01
            :ARG0 (t / team
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Los"
                        :op2 "Angeles"
                        :op3 "Lakers"))
            :ARG1 (t2 / territory
                  :mod (h / hostile))
            :time (l / last)
            :manner (t3 / tie-01
                  :ARG1 t
                  :ARG2 (s / series)))
      :snt2 (b / be-located-at-91
            :ARG1 (f / facility
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Alamodome"))
            :ARG2 (l2 / location))
      :snt3 (a / and
            :op1 (f2 / final
                  :part-of (c / conference
                        :mod (w / world-region
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "West")))
                  :domain (r / round))
            :op2 (t4 / tie-01
                  :ARG1 t
                  :ARG2 (n4 / number))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok violent clashes between the supporters of outgoing prime minister khaleda zia and opposition activists on friday left three people dead and another ### injured , news reports said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (r / report-01
            :mod (n / news))
      :ARG1 (l / leave-13
            :ARG0 (c / clash-01
                  :ARG0 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (s2 / support-01
                              :ARG1 (p2 / person
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Khaleda"
                                          :op2 "Zia")
                                    :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                          :ARG2 (m / minister
                                                :mod (p3 / prime))
                                          :time (o / outgoing)))))
                  :ARG1 (a / activist
                        :ARG0-of (o2 / oppose-01))
                  :mod (v / violent)
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (f / friday)))
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (d2 / die-01
                        :ARG1 (p4 / person
                              :quant 3))
                  :op2 (ii / injure-01
                        :ARG1 (p5 / person
                              :mod (a3 / another))))))

                                          :mod (f / federal))))))))

                              :name (n4 / name

# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (m / media
            :ARG1-of (l / local-02))
      :ARG1 (a / arrest-01
            :ARG1 (m2 / man
                  :quant 4)
            :ARG2 (t / try-01
                  :ARG0 m2
                  :ARG1 (d / detonate-01
                        :ARG0 m2
                        :ARG1 (b / bomb)
                        :location (o / outside
                              :op1 (t2 / temple
                                    :mod (r2 / religious-group
                                          :name (n / name
                                                :op1 "Jew"))))))
            :location (c / city
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "New"
                        :op2 "York"))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (w / wednesday)
                  :dayperiod (e / evening))))

# ::alignments
(h / have-concession-91
      :ARG1 (s / survive-01
            :ARG0 (e / everyone
                  :location (a / aircraft-type
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Jetliner")
                        :ARG0-of (c / carry-01
                              :ARG1 (p / person
                                    :mod (p2 / political-movement
                                          :name n
                                          :op1 "Democratic"
                                          :op2 "Party"))))))
      :manner (j / jump-03
            :ARG0 e
            :destination (s2 / safe-01
                  :ARG1 e)
            :time (m / moment
                  :time-of (b / before
                        :op1 (b2 / burst-02
                              :ARG1 a
                              :ARG2 (f / flame-01
                                    :ARG1 a))))
            :ARG1-of (r / remarkable-02))
      :ARG2 (s3 / skid-01
            :ARG1 a
            :direction (o / off
                  :op1 (r2 / runway))
            :time (l / land-01
                  :ARG1 (j2 / jetliner
                        :manner (t / thunderstorm)))))

            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "White"
                  :op2 "House"))
      :ARG1 (p / phone-01
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Abdullah")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Saudi"
                                    :op2 "Arabia"))
                        :ARG2 (k / king)))
            :ARG1 (p3 / person
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "George"
                        :op2 "W."
                        :op3 "Bush")
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (w / we)
                        :ARG2 (p4 / president)))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / saturday))
            :time (a / after
                  :op1 (u / unleash-01
                        :ARG0 (c2 / country
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Israel"))
                        :ARG1 (s3 / strike-01
                              :ARG0 c2
                              :ARG1 (t / target
                                    :location (s4 / strip
                                          :mod (g2 / gaza)))
                              :ARG0-of (p5 / punish-01))))))

# ::id 1915 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok president thabo mbeki has sent a letter to western leaders trying to allay concerns that a planned peer-review system to ensure african governments are democratic and honest was being watered down .
# ::alignments
(s / send-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Thabo"
                  :op2 "Mbeki")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG1 (l / letter)
      :ARG2 (p3 / person
            :ARG0-of (l2 / lead-02)
            :mod (w / world-region
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "West")))
      :purpose (t / try-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (a / allay-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (c / concern-01
                        :ARG0 (w2 / water-down-02
                              :ARG1 (s2 / system
                                    :mod (r / review-01
                                          :ARG1 (p4 / peer))
                                    :ARG1-of (p5 / plan-01)
                                    :purpose (e / ensure-01
                                          :ARG1 (a2 / and
                                                :op1 (d / democratic
                                                      :domain (g / government-organization
                                                            :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01
                                                                  :ARG1 (c2 / continent
                                                                        :name (n3 / name
                                                                              :op1 "Africa"))))
                                                      :op2 (h2 / honest-01
                                                            :ARG0 g))))
                                    :ARG0-of e))))))

# ::id 1917 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok russian president dmitry medvedev has hotly rejected criticism of his country as authoritarian , calling it a young democracy at the very beginning of its development .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (r / reject-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Dmitry"
                        :op2 "Medvedev")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Russia"))
                        :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
            :ARG1 (c2 / criticize-01
                  :ARG1 (c3 / country
                        :poss p)
                  :ARG2 (a2 / authoritarian))
            :manner (h2 / hotly))
      :op2 (c4 / call-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 c3
            :ARG2 (d / democracy
                  :mod (y / young))
            :time (b / begin-01
                  :ARG1 (d2 / develop-02
                        :ARG1 c3)
                  :mod (v / very))))

# ::id 1918 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the u.s. dollar gained against the new taiwan dollar on the taipei foreign exchange tuesday , increasing nt$ #.### to close at nt$ ##.### .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (g / gain-01
            :ARG1 (d / dollar
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "U.S.")))
            :ARG2 (d2 / dollar
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Taiwan"))
                  :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01))
            :time (d3 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / tuesday))
            :location (e / exchange-01
                  :mod (f / foreign)
                  :mod c))
      :op2 (ii / increase-01
            :ARG1 d
            :ARG2 (m / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (d4 / dollar)))
      :op3 (c3 / close-03
            :ARG1 d
            :ARG2 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit d4)
            :ARG1-of (ii2 / important-01)))

# ::id 1919 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok asian stocks extended their new year 's rally wednesday , with japan 's index up nearly # percent , on hopes that stimulus measures from a new u.s. administration would help speed the world 's economic recovery .
# ::alignments
(e / extend-01
      :ARG0 (s / stock
            :mod (c / continent
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Asia")))
      :ARG1 (r / rally-01
            :ARG1 s
            :time (y / year
                  :ARG1-of (n2 / new-01)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (w / wednesday))
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (h / hope-01
                  :ARG0 s
                  :ARG1 (h2 / help-01
                        :ARG0 (m / measure-02
                              :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                                    :ARG0-of (a / administrate-01)
                                    :mod (c3 / country
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "U.S.")))
                              :ARG1 (s2 / stimulate-01))
                        :ARG1 (s3 / speed-01
                              :ARG0 m
                              :ARG1 (r2 / recover-01
                                    :ARG1 (e2 / economy
                                          :poss (w2 / world))))))))
